input: Subject: A sleek modern library; Characteristics: glass shelves and minimalist furniture; Timing and lighting: daytime with ample natural light; Background: quiet reading areas and open spaces; Feeling: scholarly and calm.
output: A sleek modern library bathed in soft, diffused daylight streaming through floor-to-ceiling glass walls, its meticulously curated shelves lining minimalist wooden tables. Quiet reading corners surrounded by plush upholstered chairs and large potted plants fill the space, evoking a serene scholarly ambiance.
